px 0px; text-indent: 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px;\">　　1.报名资格：</span></p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; text-indent: 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px;\">　　（1）生产厂家或生产厂家委托参与遴选报名的委托人。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; text-indent: 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px;\">　　（2）营业执照、医疗器械生产许可证、医疗器械经营许可证、医疗器械注册证等证件齐全且在有效期内。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; text-indent: 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px;\">　　2.报名方式：邮箱报名。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; text-indent: 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px;\">　　3.报名时间：即日起到2024年</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px;\">8</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px;\">月</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px;\">1</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px;\">日17：00前。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; text-indent: 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px;\">　　4.报名所需材料</span></p><p 