/a></p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; text-indent: 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px;\">（5）遴选时间：电话另行通知</span></p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; text-indent: 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px;\">（6）联系方式：18961986565韩老师</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 16px;\"><img style=\"vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 2px;\" src=\"/ueditor/dialogs<!--#p8_attach#-->/fileTypeImages/icon_doc.gif\" src=\"/ueditor/dialogs<!--#p8_attach#-->/fileTypeImages/icon_doc.gif\" /><a style=\"font-size:12px; color:#0066cc;\" href=\"<!--#p8_attach#-->/cms/item/2024_07/26_10/2ab8a1b3bd107f2e.docx\" title=\"盐城市第一人民医院遴选项目报名表.docx\">盐城市第一人民医院遴选项目报名表.docx</a></p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; text-indent: 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px;\"><br /></span></strong><br /></p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p></p><p><br /></p>','','','','','');
